The name of the group for transaction local caches is transaction-group . This name must be
used to configure transaction local caches as shown in the following example:
curam.cache.transaction-group.curam.myproject.mycache.timeToLive=60
curam.cache.transaction-group.curam.myproject.mycache.timeToIdle=10
